datastring.dstemplatestring:
ON OCTOBER 23,2019, THE PATIENT WAS ADMITTED TO OUR HOSPITAL,AND RECEIVED
CEMIPLIMAB. ON OCTOBER 24,2019, SHE COMPLAINED OF PAIN OF MULTIPLE JOINTS AND
FEVER, AND WAS DIAGNOSED AS ARTHRITIS. WE SUSPECTED THAT THE SYMPTOM WAS
DUE TO IRAE OF CEMIPLIMAB, ELONGATED HER HOSPITALIZAION, AND PLANED TO
ADMINISTRATE PREDONISOLONE TO HER FROM OCTOBER 25,2019. FROM OCT 25,2019,
SHE
HAS BEEN TAKING PREDNISOLONE(5MG/DAY) FOR ARTHRITIS AND THE SYMPTOMS WERE
IMPROVED GRADUALLY. ON NOV 1,2019, SHE WAS DISCHARGED FROM THE HOSPITAL.
